name: PEANUT64's Projects
body:
### Welcome to peanut64's project page
This is my project page. It lists all of the projects which are hosted here on GitHub.

### Projects
* JinCAL - A simple Inventory application which also has a calendar and post-it's.
* WiTalk - The idea for this Android App was originally to allow instant messaging over WiFi. However, it will also support IM and voice messaging over the Internet in the future.

### Support or Contact
Need to contact the developer(s)? Email me at 64peanuts@gmail.com
